will be paid before I assume the duties of the position. (2021-05-01)",{"description":35,"appointee_id":36,"dsid":104,"endnote":7,"entity_id":38,"id":134,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":45,"metadata":135,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},20070,"Pursuant to the partnership agreement, following my withdrawal from the firm, I will receive a lump-sum payment of my capital account. The loan financiang the capital account will be paid off with the distribution from the capital account when I leave the firm. This payment will be calculated as of the date of my withdrawal. (2021-05-01)",{"description":35,"appointee_id":36,"dsid":104,"endnote":7,"entity_id":38,"id":137,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":51,"metadata":138,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},20067,"Following my separation, I will receive a lump-sum distribution of my Winston & Strawn LLP, cash balance pension plan. The firm will not make further contributions after my separation. (2022-02-01)",{"description":140,"appointee_id":36,"dsid":104,"endnote":7,"entity_id":141,"id":142,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":57,"metadata":143,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},"Winston and Strawn",6079,20072,"I will continue to participate in this defined contribution plan. The plan sponsor will not make further contributions after my separation. (2021-05-01)",{"description":35,"appointee_id":36,"dsid":104,"endnote":7,"entity_id":38,"id":145,"income_amount":7,"income_category_id":7,"income_type":7,"line_no":85,"metadata":146,"value_category_id":7,"doc_id":14,"doc_url":15,"form_type":17},20071,"Upon withdrawal from my partnership, the firm will withhold an amount for reconciliations and tax payments that the firm makes on behalf of its partners. Any excess amounts withheld by the firm that end up not being used will be refunded to me no later th